From 80d0fdd1c96199e4de6b0d7ae031b9ccdb4ee786 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Z User <z@container>
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 16:22:51 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix(ui): fix WYSIWYG canvas hidden + screenshot not
 displaying

Three bugs after OverlayWysiwyg refactor:

1. Canvas WYSIWYG hidden: ScreenshotBackground used CSS grid (grid-cols-12)
   with col-span classes, but OverlayCanvas col-span didn't match.
   Fix: Replace grid with flexbox (flex-row), panel = lg:w-1/4 shrink-0,
   canvas = flex-1 min-h-[400px]. Canvas now always visible.

2. Screenshot not displaying: getBackgroundUrl() returned external URLs
   (images.unsplash.com) which are blocked by Capacitor WebView CSP.
   Fix: Replace with CSS gradients (no network needed). Custom upload
   still works via URL.createObjectURL (blob: URLs are CSP-safe).

3. Background style: Changed from backgroundImage to background shorthand
   to support both gradient (preset) and url (custom upload) values.

Fixes: 'canvas WYSIWYG untuk mapping hilang' + 'screenshot tidak tampil'
---
 src/components/OverlayCanvas.tsx        |  6 ++----
 src/components/ScreenshotBackground.tsx |  4 ++--
 src/hooks/useOverlayWysiwyg.ts          | 11 ++++++-----
 3 files changed, 10 insertions(+), 11 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/components/OverlayCanvas.tsx b/src/components/OverlayCanvas.tsx
index ee1b897..2d2702e 100644
